{"id": 2923, "genre": 1001, "title": "你对生活都有哪些独特的“最低标准”？", "description": "来说说你在日常中都有哪些与众不同的“底线”。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Printstock）", "record_count": 3557, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190427193055FmrhJfukePQGoVw3.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-29T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 342017, "content": "逃离任何消耗快乐的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647172}, {"id": 342018, "content": "不点外卖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1149020}, {"id": 343810, "content": "思想可以放飞，行为必须正直。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508716}, {"id": 342023, "content": "早上必须要吃早饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1628065}, {"id": 341777, "content": "能用浏览器就不用app", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260336}, {"id": 341781, "content": "独立思考\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646843}, {"id": 342549, "content": "一定得有梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647922}, {"id": 341783, "content": "每天都要留给自己学习自己喜爱事情的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499657}, {"id": 342563, "content": "不在床上就要把被子叠好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570383}, {"id": 342059, "content": "饭可以马马虎虎 但一定要有蛋", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362352}, {"id": 342060, "content": " 我可以没有男朋友 我希望生活的自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362352}, {"id": 342573, "content": "至少，要维持人性的善良", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541107}, {"id": 341806, "content": "一定要有自己的想法，不能被大流主导", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646863}, {"id": 341811, "content": "每天晚上睡觉都必须开小夜灯", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646865}, {"id": 341556, "content": "菜可以很难吃，甚至就酱油都行，但米饭不能难吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526887}, {"id": 341557, "content": "点外卖一定表示不吃香菜", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597047}, {"id": 341558, "content": "日子再难也不能等着别人养", "image": null, "praise_count": 597, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646436}, {"id": 341559, "content": "一定要有花", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646440}, {"id": 341560, "content": "上厕所一定需要烟+手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 99847}, {"id": 341561, "content": "放飞自己一小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1543884}, {"id": 341562, "content": "每周一定要吃一顿好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688589}, {"id": 342074, "content": "不再为不太重要的事情犹豫不决", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1361236}, {"id": 341563, "content": "买东西一定要买能力范围内最好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 198, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1053990}, {"id": 341564, "content": "必须每天听歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 142, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 342844, "content": "1.洗头时必须听歌\n2.总是喜欢闻衣服的味道\n3.间歇性踌躇满志", "image": "img/option/option/20190506164026DeJjYT1whVWozXHZ", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631482}, {"id": 341565, "content": "生活里一定要有自己的小空间，比如独立卫生间，属于自己的阳台，小客厅等", "image": null, "praise_count": 246, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391490}, {"id": 341566, "content": "吃饭的时候一定要看视频。", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646449}, {"id": 341567, "content": "一定要始终对这个世界保持好奇心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 387, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1259801}, {"id": 341568, "content": "出差住宿一定要有明窗～", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417997}, {"id": 341569, "content": "吃饭的时候一定不玩手机～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417997}, {"id": 341570, "content": "日常不说网络流行语", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417997}, {"id": 341571, "content": "每天要看书。", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1529297}, {"id": 341572, "content": "拉屎一定要抽烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568106}, {"id": 341573, "content": "每天一定要打开好奇心", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631389}, {"id": 341574, "content": "电脑桌面一定要干净，能多干净就多干净，最好一个图标都没有。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646207}, {"id": 341575, "content": "再难过也不能颓废", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537367}, {"id": 341576, "content": "早上、中午各一杯现做咖啡", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1332097}, {"id": 341577, "content": "不要葱不要葱不要葱…", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646469}, {"id": 341578, "content": "来来来，大家秀一下自己多矫情", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1432403}, {"id": 341579, "content": "绝对不要996，年轻用命换钱，年老用钱换命，意义不大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 207, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1645608}, {"id": 341580, "content": "吃的东西没过期一定要吃完", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537792}, {"id": 341581, "content": "饭可以马马虎虎吃，但一定要有蔬菜", "image": null, "praise_count": 111, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216372}, {"id": 341582, "content": "开车的时候必须有歌…", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1533703}, {"id": 349262, "content": "卫生间要有独立便器而不是沟槽式", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 341583, "content": "吃饭一定不能在电脑前或者工位上吃（打游戏不算）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382420}, {"id": 341584, "content": "可以有时间静静地玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407454}, {"id": 341585, "content": "日子再怎么不堪，都必须正常的无过滤的上网.", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613755}, {"id": 341587, "content": "睡觉的地方得是无声音，弱光，无气味", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852421}, {"id": 341588, "content": "必须要有网", "image": null, "praise_count": 108, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1562933}, {"id": 341589, "content": "书不一定每天看，但是想看书的时候马上就能拿出来看，不一定每天都要打游戏，打游戏必须玩精品一点的，浪费时间和圈钱的不要", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408819}]}